    @startuml
[*] --> SellerRegistration : [seller portal][new seller]
SellerRegistration : entry / Unregistered user
SellerRegistration : do / Get Valid Seller Credentials
SellerRegistration : exit / Seller Account Registered

SellerRegistration --> SellerVerification : Seller Account Registered
SellerVerification : entry / Verify Seller Account
SellerVerification : exit / Login Seller

SellerVerification --> SellerLogin : Seller Account Registered
SellerLogin : entry / Verify Seller Login
SellerLogin : exit / Seller Logged In Successfully

SellerLogin --> SellerHome : Seller Logged In
SellerHome : entry / Display Seller Dashboard
SellerHome : do / Manage Products
SellerHome : exit / Promote Products

SellerHome --> SaleProducts : Seller Adds New Product
SaleProducts : entry / Add Product to Seller Inventory
SaleProducts : exit / Product Added Successfully

SellerHome --> [*] : Logout

[*] --> CustomerLogin
CustomerLogin : entry / Authenticate Customer
CustomerLogin : exit / Successfully Logged In

CustomerLogin --> CustomerHome : Customer Logged In
CustomerHome : entry / Display Recommended Products
CustomerHome : do / Browse Products
CustomerHome : exit / Chat with Seller

CustomerHome --> ViewProduct : User Views Product
ViewProduct : entry / View Products
ViewProduct : do / Search for Product
ViewProduct : exit / Display Product Results

ViewProduct --> BuyProduct : User Decides to Buy
BuyProduct : entry / Select Product to Buy
BuyProduct : do / Add to Cart
BuyProduct : exit / Proceed to Checkout

BuyProduct --> MakePurchase : User Proceeds to Checkout
MakePurchase : entry / Proceed to Payment
MakePurchase : do / Complete Payment
MakePurchase : exit / Payment Successful

MakePurchase --> [*] : Logout

CustomerHome --> [*] : Logout

@enduml